Manage cert-manager resources required for TLS in the MCP platform

Usage:
  mcp-runtime cluster cert [command]

Available Commands:
  apply       Apply cert-manager resources
  status      Check cert-manager resources
  wait        Wait for registry certificate readiness

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for cert

Global Flags:
      --debug   Enable debug mode with structured error logging

Use "mcp-runtime cluster cert [command] --help" for more information about a command.
